records.addlTxt:
Arguments heard as to bail. Court ordered cash bail adjusted down to $1,500.00 with turnover to Justice Point monitoring with the following conditions:
-Defendant to be in his residence Monday-Friday from the hours of 10:00 p.m. to 9:00 a.m. Defendant to be in his residence Saturday and Sunday from the hours of 7:00 p.m. to 9:00 a.m.;
-Defendant to have absolutely no contact with the victim or the address listed in the criminal complaint;
-Defendant may not possess any weapons;
-Defendant to maintain absolute sobriety;
-Do not commit any new crimes;
If defendant posts bail, defense counsel to bring written confirmation of defendant's employment to the next court date.
